This means you get challenegs/requests from validators but the reults/scores from the first 192 miners are not joined (self.new_pow_benchmark does not exist anymore for the first 192 uid's). Why 192? Only the last 64 threads are joined because: the self.validator_challenge_batch_size = 64 and 256 - 64 = 192.
So self.threads = [] needs to be outside the first for loop
